== Description == [[Image:Redoom_MAP01.pngâ€Ž|right|thumb|230px|RAP01 Start Area]] Redoom is a simple and small 5-level wad inspired by Knee-Deep in ZDoom, it is about a remake of 4 levels (with 1 secret level) of Doom 2 adding new rooms, for single player only, each level is the first one of every episode: * RAP01: Remake of MAP01, it is totally new level with the same theme of MAP01. * RAP02: Remake of MAP07, it has a lava theme. * RAP03: Remake of MAP12, a mix between MAP06 and MAP12. * RAP04: Remake of MAP21. * RAP05: Secret level, not a remake.
== Features == * Skulltag's monster [[Classes:Belphegor|Belphegor]] is in this wad. * A new difficulty called: Redoom Special (Respawn is removed of the difficulty because it would be impossible to finish the wad, especially RAP02, the player would face infinite wave). * 5 levels with a secret.
